r's wedding."],[4517,4658,"Then you have an invitation?"],[4771,4934,"Block us again and I will make sure"],[4967,5042,"you're fired."],[5280,5401,"Why are you still here?"],[5480,5693,"Oh, hi! Nat!"],[5693,5793,"Tell them,"],[5793,5926,"I'm your sister."],[6047,6139,"Right!"],[6160,6473,"How dare they block family from entering?"],[6802,6873,"I'm sorry."],[6952,7069,"I don't know you."]],"81":[[116,241,"Go ahead and get ready, babe."],[316,392,"I'll deal with them."],[875,1005,"Natalie!"],[1005,1101,"We're your family!"],[1301,1380,"Family?"],[1413,1501,"Tell me, was she family"],[1501,1551,"when you were"],[1551,1634,"bending over backwards"],[1634,1697,"for Vanessa?"],[1793,1822,"Or,"],[1864,2031,"was she family when you left her out of"],[2031,2097,"your inheritance?"],[2235,2318,"Rhett,"],[2348,2535,"we can't let the little things ruin us."],[2565,2690,"You're our brother-in-law,"],[2690,2773,"after all."],[2773,2852,"Yeah."],[2919,3036,"You're a billionaire."],[3069,3153,"Natalie has"],[3153,3257,"everything she needs."],[3257,3378,"I mean, it's only fair you"],[3407,3495,"take care of us."],[3595,3716,"You guys are shameless."],[3803,3887,"You guys are literally"],[3887,3958,"the worst people"],[3958,4112,"I've ever met in my entire life."],[4112,4175,"The only reason"],[4175,4250,"you're crawling back to me"],[4250,4375,"is because you found out who I am."],[4396,4587,"Well, it's your wedding day."],[4642,4788,"Isn't that when you're supposed to"],[4813,4909,"let the past go"],[4909,5138,"and come together as a family?"],[5159,5230,"No."],[5251,5438,"No, absolutely not."],[5438,5559,"Ellie and Natalie..."],[5634,5722,"are my family,"],[5793,5951,"and I will do everything I can to"],[5951,6101,"protect and provide for them"],[6101,6210,"for the rest of my life."],[6272,6343,"But you people?"],[6414,6606,"I want nothing to do with you people."],[6702,6756,"Please,"],[6840,6952,"we're sorry."],[6952,7052,"I mean, you can't just"],[7115,7215,"abandon us like this."],[7215,7282,"I mean, you're our"],[7311,7419,"brother-in-law after all."],[7540,7624,"Didn't you hear me?"],[7820,7957,"I said stay away from Natalie."],[8012,8166,"I'm gonna make sure every business tie"],[8166,8287,"you guys have is severed."],[8308,8433,"No, no."],[8491,8604,"Security!"],[8604,8679,"What?"],[8721,8787,"Get them out of here."],[8875,9025,"This is madness."],[9025,9050,"I'm sorry."],[9050,9154,"There must be some sort of"],[9180,9230,"misunderstanding."],[9309,9367,"Hey, wait."],[9367,9534,"Get your hands off me."],[9534,9630,"I am a senator!"]],"82":[[1780,2035,"It's now time to exchange your rings."],[4996,5088,"At this time,"],[5155,5305,"Natalie and Rhett"],[5380,5534,"will share the vows they wrote"],[5584,5647,"for each other."]],"83":[[196,300,"From the day we met,"],[404,617,"the words I heard from you most were,"],[663,763,"don't worry."],[934,1117,"Somehow that meant more to me than"],[1117,1242,"I love you."],[1343,1497,"It meant I was safe."],[1643,1718,"It meant you would"],[1718,1843,"always look out for me."],[2085,2164,"You..."],[2281,2369,"and Ellie"],[2656,2898,"made me believe I was worth loving."],[3032,3119,"And I promise"],[3119,3265,"I will cherish and"],[3265,3365,"love you both,"],[3407,3503,"forever."],[3628,3782,"Natalie, you're the most extraordinary"],[3782,3949,"woman I've ever met in my entire life."],[4062,4133,"You're brilliant."],[4229,4300,"You're beautiful."],[4437,4500,"You're kind."],[4612,4683,"I'm Natalie."],[4750,4867,"It's nice to meet you."],[6181,6256,"I love you."],[6448,6535,"I can't wait to spend"],[6535,6681,"the rest of my life with you,"],[6785,6831,"forever."],[7157,7290,"You may now kiss one another."]]}